lead_paragraph: Failed 2012 U.S. Republican presidential nominee Mitt Romney said on Sunday he expects Hillary Clinton to win or lose the White House on her record, not that of her husband, former Democratic President Bill Clinton and his sexual indiscretions.

headline.main: Romney Says He Expects Hillary Clinton to Run on Her Own Record
headline.print_headline: Romney Says He Expects Hillary Clinton to Run on Her Own Record
